          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Spam Calls Task Force Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Justice to assemble an interagency working group to study and report to Congress on the enforcement of the prohibition&nbsp;against certain robocalls. Specifically, the working group&nbsp;must look into how to better enforce against robocalls by examining issues&nbsp;such as&nbsp;the types of laws, policies, or constraints that could be inhibiting enforcement.</p>]]></text>
